ANTIBIOTIC RESISTANT ACINETOBACTER - NEW ZEALAND
************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Antibiotic resistance, beta lactamase, Acinetobact... 971125221014
